data.description: Welcome to your new HOME SWEET HOME! Situated on a spacious corner lot this traditional 2-story home has so much to offer! You are welcomed into this home where you'll find a formal dining room and office conveniently situated near the entrance. Leading into the family room, the gas burning fireplace acts as a wonderful focal point and gives this home a warm and inviting feel. Seamless connection to the family room, kitchen and breakfast nook, make for easy entertaining and gathering. Retreat to the primary bedroom conveniently located on the main floor with an en suite featuring double vanities, an oversized shower and separate garden tub. Three sizable bedrooms complete the interior of this home, each with their own large windows allowing natural light to pour in. Turn this backyard into your own personal retreat in the city. With a covered patio, in-ground pool and oversized yard, this backyard will be one for entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your next home!
